Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Visit of Japanese emperor
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z91w9
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Oct 1975
Increased security surrounds visit of Japanese emperor, following attempts on President Ford's life. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less